<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-765] Performance regression in PDFBox 1.2.0</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-765</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Arjohn Kampman reported a notable performance drop in PDFBox 1.2.0, possibly caused by &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-754&quot; title=&quot;Move Resources to org.apache.pdfbox.resources&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-754&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-754&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
